SimplyHired,is,an,online,recruiting,solution,that,serves,over,million,people,and,thousands,of,employers,across,countries,The,site,offers,an,extensive,job,search,tool,searchable,by,both,job,title,and,locations,as,well,as,allowing,additional,filters,to,refine,searches,The,SImplyHired,Job,API,allows,developers,and,web,publishers,to,create,custom,job,search,tools,widgets,and,mashups,using,the,database,of,over,million,jobs,Select,partners,who,utilize,the,API,can,join,the,affiliate,program,and,monetize,third,party,sites